{
  "stem": "19195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A10,862.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had it taken out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, because I kind of landed a good job in Miami Beach.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Have you ever heard of the Famous Restaurant?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I worked there 28 years.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only I would watch over myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Be-- be-- there was no such thing who watched over me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you were unable to do it for yourself, they would release you right away from the lines and take you right away to the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they enlightened us, the Polish girls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You think this is bad?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had it worse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have it good now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- it was just their [? fun ?] time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES] There was a guard in-- a-- a Gestapo in Auschwitz and Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name was Bogar.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He always walked around with a cane.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- he-- he would say, hey Jew, come on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I want to tell you something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that man right away, because he walked around with a cane, he-- he broke his cane we don't know how many times.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because that's how we-- he would beat up the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For no reason.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not by him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The one I really, really despised, and I do till this day, is the one who took me away from my mother.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was at a trial in-- in Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't want to-- I never-- I promised myself I'll never set foot in Germany in my life.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But being bothered, being called from the judge at Frankfurt of the Auschwitz trial, [PAUSES] I decided finally to go.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What would we talk-- how long can we live like this?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How long do you think we'll be alive like this?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And chances were very slim of surviving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I came once very close.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
